1
00:00:04,720 --> 00:00:05,880
[Wharf]
[Lee Hyun Jun: Have you been to Nami Island?]

2
00:00:05,880 --> 00:00:07,480
[Kim Sun Wook: No, it's my first time.]

3
00:00:07,720 --> 00:00:10,480
[Kim Sun Wook: Have you?]
[Lee Hyun Jun: When I was really young.]

4
00:00:10,480 --> 00:00:12,360
[Lee Hyun Jun: With my family.
But I don't remember much.]

5
00:00:12,360 --> 00:00:14,320
[Lee Hyun Jun: I only remember going there.]

6
00:00:14,320 --> 00:00:18,440
[Lee Hyun Jun: I don't remember what I did there.]

7
00:00:19,320 --> 00:00:23,360
[Kim Sun Wook: I have many firsts with you.]

8
00:00:32,520 --> 00:00:34,160
[Kim Sun Wook: Is that it?]

9
00:00:38,920 --> 00:00:40,760
[Kim Sun Wook: The trails are beautiful.]

10
00:00:41,360 --> 00:00:42,800
[Kim Sun Wook: They're taking pictures.]

11
00:00:44,080 --> 00:00:47,840
[Lee Hyun Jun: There's the Grim Reaper.]
[Kim Sun Wook: Halloween was quite a while ago.]

12
00:00:48,280 --> 00:00:49,440
[Kim Sun Wook: Christmas is coming.]

13
00:00:49,440 --> 00:00:51,240
[Kim Sun Wook:
I think it'll still be hanging then.]

14
00:00:51,240 --> 00:00:54,720
[Lee Hyun Jun: It's even wearing a winter scarf.]

15
00:00:55,440 --> 00:00:58,480
[Together again,
what kind of date will they have?]

16
00:00:55,520 --> 00:00:56,360
Cute.

17
00:00:59,720 --> 00:01:04,560
[Lee Hyun Jun: I came here
when I was little. I had a lot of fun.]

18
00:01:05,239 --> 00:01:08,120
[Lee Hyun Jun: When I was
in kindergarten, or a bit older than that.]

19
00:01:10,480 --> 00:01:13,360
[Lee Hyun Jun: Have you been here before?]
[Kim Sun Wook: No, it's my first time.]

20
00:01:12,330 --> 00:01:12,990
Really?

21
00:01:13,360 --> 00:01:16,080
[Kim Sun Wook: So it's more interesting.]

22
00:01:17,120 --> 00:01:18,920
[Kim Sun Wook: It's my first time on Nami Island.]

23
00:01:18,920 --> 00:01:22,640
[Kim Sun Wook: Last time we went on a date,
it was also my first time going to a roller rink.]

24
00:01:22,640 --> 00:01:24,520
[Kim Sun Wook: Both times were firsts.]

25
00:01:25,120 --> 00:01:27,720
[Kim Sun Wook: So it was meaningful to me.]

26
00:01:30,580 --> 00:01:33,259
[Lee Hyun Jun: (Sun Wook) said
it's his first time visiting Nami Island.]

27
00:01:33,780 --> 00:01:35,539
[Lee Hyun Jun: It feels quite exciting,]

28
00:01:35,740 --> 00:01:39,780
[Lee Hyun Jun: since it's his first with me.]

29
00:01:40,520 --> 00:01:41,509
Do we have to see the animals?

30
00:01:41,380 --> 00:01:45,660
[The two enjoying their first together]

31
00:01:41,920 --> 00:01:42,850
Yes, of course.

32
00:01:50,259 --> 00:01:51,500
[Lee Hyun Jun: This is real glass.]

33
00:01:51,500 --> 00:01:52,460
[Kim Sun Wook: It's real glass?]

34
00:01:52,460 --> 00:01:54,100
[Lee Hyun Jun: Real soju bottles.]

35
00:01:54,300 --> 00:01:55,820
[Really?]
[Yeah.]

36
00:01:55,820 --> 00:01:58,539
[Kim Sun Wook: It looks real.]
[Lee Hyun Jun: It's real.]

37
00:01:58,539 --> 00:02:00,140
[Lee Hyun Jun: It's really real.]

38
00:02:00,140 --> 00:02:02,340
[Kim Sun Wook: How did they make it?]

39
00:02:03,060 --> 00:02:06,060
[Lee Hyun Jun: Melt it with heat, I guess?]

40
00:02:06,060 --> 00:02:09,820
[Lee Hyun Jun: I touched it just now.]
[Kim Sun Wook: Really?]

41
00:02:09,820 --> 00:02:12,020
[Kim Sun Wook: There's so much trash.]

42
00:02:14,180 --> 00:02:16,300
[Lee Hyun Jun: This isn't right.]

43
00:02:15,470 --> 00:02:16,210
Yeah.

44
00:02:16,900 --> 00:02:19,900
[Kim Sun Wook: "This isn't right," haha.]
[Lee Hyun Jun: What's wrong?]

45
00:02:19,900 --> 00:02:23,460
[Kim Sun Wook: You sound so virtuous.]

46
00:02:24,060 --> 00:02:25,780
[Lee Hyun Jun: I am a virtuous person.]

47
00:02:27,500 --> 00:02:30,620
[Lee Hyun Jun: Let me take a picture of you.]
[Kim Sun Wook: Of me?]

48
00:02:28,800 --> 00:02:29,740
Yeah.

49
00:02:31,079 --> 00:02:31,950
OK.

50
00:02:33,420 --> 00:02:35,900
[Kim Sun Wook: Let's take a photo together after.]
[Lee Hyun Jun: OK.]

51
00:02:35,900 --> 00:02:37,980
[Kim Sun Wook: How should I pose?]

52
00:02:38,020 --> 00:02:39,500
[Thinking]

53
00:02:40,540 --> 00:02:42,220
[Kim Sun Wook: Lean like this?]

54
00:02:42,220 --> 00:02:43,620
[Lee Hyun Jun: Be careful. Don't fall.]

55
00:02:43,620 --> 00:02:46,980
[Kim Sun Wook: Don't fall... I can't fall.]

56
00:02:49,340 --> 00:02:51,660
[Lee Hyun Jun: You look good.]
[Kim Sun Wook: Yeah?]

57
00:02:50,829 --> 00:02:51,560
Yeah.

58
00:02:52,780 --> 00:02:53,700
[Lee Hyun Jun: So cute.]

59
00:02:53,700 --> 00:02:54,900
[Surprised]

60
00:02:53,850 --> 00:02:54,540
What?

61
00:02:55,540 --> 00:02:57,300
[Lee Hyun Jun: You look cute.]

62
00:02:57,620 --> 00:02:59,300
[Kim Sun Wook: Oh? What's with him?]

63
00:02:59,300 --> 00:03:00,740
[Kim Sun Wook: What is he doing?]

64
00:03:01,100 --> 00:03:05,140
[Kim Sun Wook: When we're alone,
he talks a lot, and is very cutesy]

65
00:03:05,140 --> 00:03:06,620
[Kim Sun Wook: and affectionate.]

66
00:03:08,700 --> 00:03:13,540
[Kim Sun Wook: I think... he is a gentle person.]

67
00:03:13,540 --> 00:03:16,340
[Kim Sun Wook: He's more gentle than I thought.]

68
00:03:16,860 --> 00:03:18,579
[Shy]

69
00:03:18,660 --> 00:03:20,380
[Kim Sun Wook: Let's take photos together.]

70
00:03:21,579 --> 00:03:24,180
[Making memories together]

71
00:03:21,600 --> 00:03:22,850
-Like this. -I'm afraid I'll fall.

72
00:03:22,850 --> 00:03:23,540
Be careful.

73
00:03:24,579 --> 00:03:26,980
[Lee Hyun Jun: Not bad, right?]
[Kim Sun Wook: You look good on camera.]

74
00:03:26,980 --> 00:03:28,060
[Lee Hyun Jun: You too.]

75
00:03:28,060 --> 00:03:29,140
[Kim Sun Wook: You're more photogenic.]

76
00:03:29,820 --> 00:03:30,980
[Lee Hyun Jun:
You're like a roasted chestnut seller.]

77
00:03:30,980 --> 00:03:32,140
[Kim Sun Wook: Chestnut seller...]

78
00:03:32,340 --> 00:03:33,500
[Lee Hyun Jun:
Like you'd sell roasted sweet potatoes.]

79
00:03:33,500 --> 00:03:36,260
[Kim Sun Wook: Should I take it off?]
[Lee Hyun Jun: No, it's cute. It suits you.]

80
00:03:36,250 --> 00:03:37,010
Really?

81
00:03:37,340 --> 00:03:39,100
[Touching]

82
00:03:40,180 --> 00:03:42,540
[Lee Hyun Jun: We walked and talked,]

83
00:03:42,540 --> 00:03:44,380
[Lee Hyun Jun: and took photos for each other.]

84
00:03:44,380 --> 00:03:46,380
[Lee Hyun Jun: It was an enjoyable date.]

85
00:03:46,380 --> 00:03:48,140
[Lee Hyun Jun: It was fun too.]

86
00:03:50,380 --> 00:03:53,300
[Lee Hyun Jun: This place is too big.
It'd be better to take that train.]

87
00:03:53,900 --> 00:03:56,500
[Kim Sun Wook:
I don't think you should ride that.]

88
00:03:57,700 --> 00:03:58,940
[Kim Sun Wook: It doesn't suit you...]

89
00:03:58,660 --> 00:03:58,920
Why?

90
00:03:58,940 --> 00:04:00,980
[Kim Sun Wook: I don't think you should.]

91
00:04:00,020 --> 00:04:00,730
Why?

92
00:04:00,980 --> 00:04:03,260
[Lee Hyun Jun: Why can't I?]

93
00:04:03,260 --> 00:04:05,540
[Lee Hyun Jun: Can't I ride it?]

94
00:04:05,820 --> 00:04:07,700
[Kim Sun Wook: Let's ride it together.]

95
00:04:07,700 --> 00:04:10,220
[Lee Hyun Jun: Forget it.]
[Kim Sun Wook: No, let's ride it.]

96
00:04:09,520 --> 00:04:10,220
I don't wanna.

97
00:04:10,220 --> 00:04:13,540
[Lee Hyun Jun: I'll hang onto the back.]

98
00:04:16,339 --> 00:04:18,180
[Kim Sun Wook: Yay, pizza.]

99
00:04:18,180 --> 00:04:20,220
[Lee Hyun Jun: What did I do
when I came here as a kid?]

100
00:04:20,220 --> 00:04:21,860
[Kim Sun Wook: I feel like
you'd have went to see the ostrichs.]

101
00:04:22,380 --> 00:04:23,740
[Lee Hyun Jun: I didn't just see ostriches.]

102
00:04:23,740 --> 00:04:25,660
[Lee Hyun Jun:
There's more, but I don't remember.]

103
00:04:25,100 --> 00:04:25,900
With your family?

104
00:04:25,660 --> 00:04:28,500
[Lee Hyun Jun: I think I was
really impressed with the ostriches]

105
00:04:28,500 --> 00:04:31,300
[Lee Hyun Jun:
that it's the only thing I remember.]

106
00:04:29,450 --> 00:04:30,130
Yeah?

107
00:04:31,300 --> 00:04:34,260
[Kim Sun Wook: So you came with me this time.]

108
00:04:35,260 --> 00:04:37,500
[Lee Hyun Jun: My second time here is with you.]

109
00:04:37,540 --> 00:04:39,020
[Heh heh]

110
00:04:39,170 --> 00:04:39,980
Right.

111
00:04:40,260 --> 00:04:43,100
[Kim Sun Wook: Look over there. There are ducks.]

112
00:04:43,659 --> 00:04:45,700
[Kim Sun Wook: I like making that in winter.]

113
00:04:46,180 --> 00:04:48,060
[Lee Hyun Jun: I have a lot at home.]
[Kim Sun Wook: Really?]

114
00:04:48,060 --> 00:04:49,980
[Lee Hyun Jun:
Snow duck makers and snow Pikachu makers.]

115
00:04:50,300 --> 00:04:51,580
[Kim Sun Wook: Pikachu too?]

116
00:04:52,020 --> 00:04:53,020
[Yeah.]

117
00:04:53,020 --> 00:04:55,420
[Lee Hyun Jun: And Snow Choonsik makers.]

118
00:04:55,820 --> 00:04:59,940
[Kim Sun Wook: I've never heard of snow Pikachu.]
[Lee Hyun Jun: I got it as a gift.]

119
00:05:01,020 --> 00:05:03,340
[Kim Sun Wook:
You get a lot of Pikachu gifts, huh?]

120
00:05:03,620 --> 00:05:06,860
[Lee Hyun Jun: I think I received
more Pikachu stuff than I bought myself.]

121
00:05:08,540 --> 00:05:11,100
[Kim Sun Wook: I gave you a Pikachu yesterday.]
[Lee Hyun Jun: Yeah.]

122
00:05:11,900 --> 00:05:14,620
[Lee Hyun Jun: You have Pikachu pajamas too.]
Kim Sun Wook: Me?]

123
00:05:13,510 --> 00:05:14,370
-Yes. -And...

124
00:05:15,500 --> 00:05:17,340
[Kim Sun Wook: You saw it already, right?]

125
00:05:17,660 --> 00:05:19,740
[Yesterday morning]

126
00:05:20,540 --> 00:05:21,460
[Lee Hyun Jun: Whose Pikachu (pajamas) are these?]

127
00:05:21,900 --> 00:05:23,300
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Sun Wook's.]

128
00:05:24,500 --> 00:05:26,460
[Smiles]

129
00:05:29,100 --> 00:05:30,860
[Kim Sun Wook:
I was going to wear it and surprise you.]

130
00:05:30,860 --> 00:05:32,620
[Lee Hyun Jun: I saw it already.]

131
00:05:33,020 --> 00:05:34,220
[(Sad)]
[Kim Sun Wook: I blew it.]

132
00:05:34,220 --> 00:05:35,580
[Lee Hyun Jun: How?]

133
00:05:35,580 --> 00:05:37,900
[Kim Sun Wook: You found out
before I could surprise you.]

134
00:05:39,100 --> 00:05:40,659
[(Melting at his cuteness)]
[Lee Hyun Jun: It doesn't matter.]

135
00:05:40,860 --> 00:05:42,100
[Lee Hyun Jun: I saw it yesterday.]

136
00:05:43,100 --> 00:05:46,140
[Sun Wook's surprise was a bit of a fail]

137
00:05:47,900 --> 00:05:51,300
[Kim Sun Wook: How'd you feel
when I asked you out on a date yesterday?]

138
00:05:52,140 --> 00:05:53,260
[Lee Hyun Jun: When you asked me out?]

139
00:05:53,040 --> 00:05:53,320
Yeah.

140
00:05:53,260 --> 00:05:54,420
[Lee Hyun Jun: I was surprised.]

141
00:05:54,420 --> 00:05:56,659
[Lee Hyun Jun: I never imagined that]

142
00:05:56,659 --> 00:05:59,940
[Lee Hyun Jun: you'd give me back
the card I gave you.]

143
00:06:00,260 --> 00:06:02,300
[Kim Sun Wook: Really?]

144
00:06:02,300 --> 00:06:04,700
[Kim Sun Wook: I prepared a lot.]

145
00:06:05,980 --> 00:06:09,260
[Lee Hyun Jun: But I haven't done anything.]

146
00:06:09,380 --> 00:06:11,620
[Proud]

147
00:06:13,460 --> 00:06:15,820
[Kim Sun Wook: Thank you.]

148
00:06:15,040 --> 00:06:15,970
Please enjoy.

149
00:06:15,970 --> 00:06:16,960
Thank you.

150
00:06:23,020 --> 00:06:25,580
[Kim Sun Wook: What are you gonna eat first?]
[Lee Hyun Jun: Pepperoni.]

151
00:06:25,580 --> 00:06:26,860
[Kim Sun Wook: Pepperoni pizza?]

152
00:06:28,980 --> 00:06:31,860
[Kim Sun Wook: So you like Pepperoni pizza.]
[Lee Hyun Jun: It's my favorite.]

153
00:06:31,860 --> 00:06:33,620
[Kim Sun Wook: I thought so too.]

154
00:06:34,060 --> 00:06:36,540
[Kim Sun Wook: We're prospective mukbang stars.]

155
00:06:36,740 --> 00:06:38,380
[Lee Hyun Jun: Two big eaters.]
[Kim Sun Wook: Totally.]

156
00:06:39,220 --> 00:06:40,500
[Kim Sun Wook: It looks so good.]

157
00:06:44,780 --> 00:06:47,270
[Kim Sun Wook: It's delicious.]
[Lee Hyun Jun: Yeah?]

158
00:06:47,920 --> 00:06:50,480
[Kim Sun Wook: Do you like Western food?]

159
00:06:50,480 --> 00:06:52,640
[Lee Hyun Jun: Western food?]

160
00:06:52,890 --> 00:06:54,690
[Lee Hyun Jun: I do,]

161
00:06:54,690 --> 00:06:57,090
[Lee Hyun Jun: but I like Korean food the most.]

162
00:06:57,409 --> 00:06:59,409
[Kim Sun Wook: I'm sad about this shoot's dorm.]

163
00:06:59,770 --> 00:07:01,570
[Lee Hyun Jun: Because you can't cook?]
[Kim Sun Wook: Yeah.]

164
00:07:02,090 --> 00:07:03,950
[Kim Sun Wook:
I wanted to make spicy braised chicken.]

165
00:07:03,950 --> 00:07:05,810
[Lee Hyun Jun: Really?]

166
00:07:06,370 --> 00:07:08,890
[Lee Hyun Jun: I like spicy braised chicken.]

167
00:07:09,610 --> 00:07:13,370
[Kim Sun Wook: So I even found a recipe.]

168
00:07:13,370 --> 00:07:16,690
[Kim Sun Wook: But we can't cook this time.]

169
00:07:17,220 --> 00:07:19,340
[Sad]

170
00:07:20,320 --> 00:07:23,000
[Kim Sun Wook: Have you read my letter?]
[Lee Hyun Jun: Yeah.]

171
00:07:23,000 --> 00:07:24,960
[Lee Hyun Jun: Alone in the corner.]

172
00:07:25,280 --> 00:07:30,160
[Lee Hyun Jun: What a huge contrast.
I only gave you two shoe charms.]

173
00:07:26,320 --> 00:07:26,650
What?

174
00:07:30,160 --> 00:07:32,560
[Kim Sun Wook: You?]
[(Nods)]

175
00:07:32,560 --> 00:07:34,240
[Lee Hyun Jun: Did you know it was me?]

176
00:07:34,240 --> 00:07:36,600
[Kim Sun Wook: I knew it right away.]
[Lee Hyun Jun: How?]

177
00:07:36,960 --> 00:07:40,200
[Kim Sun Wook: You're the only one who'd give]

178
00:07:40,200 --> 00:07:42,000
[Kim Sun Wook: something so simple.]

179
00:07:42,100 --> 00:07:44,260
[Embarrassed]

180
00:07:44,880 --> 00:07:47,480
[Lee Hyun Jun: It was too simple.]

181
00:07:48,520 --> 00:07:50,520
[Kim Sun Wook: But it's cute.]

182
00:07:58,760 --> 00:08:01,720
[Lee Hyun Jun:
Did you get a lot of messages yesterday?]

183
00:08:02,200 --> 00:08:05,280
[Kim Sun Wook: Messages?
You were in my Anonymous Chat!]

184
00:08:05,540 --> 00:08:07,310
-Yeah. -My chat.

185
00:08:07,720 --> 00:08:09,240
[Lee Hyun Jun: Do you know who I was?]

186
00:08:09,640 --> 00:08:12,240
[Kim Sun Wook: Of course. Just from your tone.]
[Lee Hyun Jun: How?]

187
00:08:12,240 --> 00:08:14,160
[Lee Hyun Jun: Who was I then?]

188
00:08:14,400 --> 00:08:17,000
[Kim Sun Wook: I don't remember your nickname.]

189
00:08:17,000 --> 00:08:19,120
[Kim Sun Wook: But you didn't say much.]

190
00:08:22,560 --> 00:08:24,560
[Lee Hyun Jun: How many people
were in your chat besides me?]

191
00:08:23,870 --> 00:08:24,500
Hmm?

192
00:08:24,560 --> 00:08:26,040
[Lee Hyun Jun: How many people
were in your chat besides me?]

193
00:08:26,440 --> 00:08:28,520
[Kim Sun Wook: One other person.]
[Lee Hyun Jun: One?]

194
00:08:32,400 --> 00:08:35,039
[Kim Sun Wook:
There were four or five in your chat.]

195
00:08:37,520 --> 00:08:41,120
[Lee Hyun Jun: Four, including you, I think.]

196
00:08:44,020 --> 00:08:45,580
[Thinking]

197
00:08:45,580 --> 00:08:47,440
[Lee Hyun Jun: I have no idea who they were.]

198
00:08:48,780 --> 00:08:52,040
[Kim Sun Wook: I have an idea.]

199
00:08:52,180 --> 00:08:55,480
[Lee Hyun Jun: How do you know?]
[Kim Sun Wook: It's quite obvious.]

200
00:08:55,860 --> 00:08:58,600
[Lee Hyun Jun: Who were they?
Who do you think they were?]

201
00:09:00,600 --> 00:09:02,040
[Kim Sun Wook: Well...]

202
00:09:02,520 --> 00:09:04,240
[Lee Hyun Jun: Who?]

203
00:09:06,000 --> 00:09:08,440
[Kim Sun Wook: Your... Your first roommate.]

204
00:09:08,440 --> 00:09:13,640
[Lee Hyun Jun: Yun Jae?]
[Kim Sun Wook: Yeah, I think Yun Jae was in it.]

205
00:09:12,550 --> 00:09:13,300
Yeah?

206
00:09:14,520 --> 00:09:19,080
[Kim Sun Wook: Actually,
I haven't talked much with Yun Jae,]

207
00:09:19,080 --> 00:09:20,720
[Kim Sun Wook: but I could already tell.]

208
00:09:20,920 --> 00:09:22,000
[Last morning]

209
00:09:22,420 --> 00:09:24,020
[Smoothly]

210
00:09:24,300 --> 00:09:25,460
[Peeping]

211
00:09:26,120 --> 00:09:29,320
[Kim Sun Wook: I can't help but notice it.]

212
00:09:30,240 --> 00:09:32,520
[Kim Sun Wook: Who were you]

213
00:09:32,520 --> 00:09:34,600
[Kim Sun Wook: curious about then?]

214
00:09:34,600 --> 00:09:37,320
[Kim Sun Wook: We could join two chats.]

215
00:09:39,560 --> 00:09:41,880
[Lee Hyun Jun: One... One was Han Gyeol.]

216
00:09:43,600 --> 00:09:45,760
[Lee Hyun Jun: That's only because]

217
00:09:45,760 --> 00:09:47,000
[Lee Hyun Jun: we have the same MBTI.]

218
00:09:47,400 --> 00:09:52,080
[Kim Sun Wook: Oh, really?]
[Lee Hyun Jun: I've never met an ISTJ before.]

219
00:09:52,480 --> 00:09:55,040
[Lee Hyun Jun: ISTJ is a rare MBTI.]
[Kim Sun Wook: That's true.]

220
00:09:55,040 --> 00:09:56,680
[Lee Hyun Jun: So I was intrigued.]

221
00:09:56,680 --> 00:09:58,880
[Lee Hyun Jun:
But I didn't say anything in his chat.]

222
00:09:59,240 --> 00:10:00,280
[Lee Hyun Jun: I just watched.]

223
00:10:00,280 --> 00:10:01,520
[Kim Sun Wook: Actually,]

224
00:10:01,520 --> 00:10:03,240
[Kim Sun Wook: I only went into]

225
00:10:03,240 --> 00:10:05,080
[Kim Sun Wook: one chat that day.]

226
00:10:05,080 --> 00:10:09,400
[Kim Sun Wook:
But I was curious about Han Gyeol's chat.]

227
00:10:10,000 --> 00:10:12,320
[Kim Sun Wook: Since he's popular.]

228
00:10:12,720 --> 00:10:15,400
[Kim Sun Wook: I sensed that he's popular,]

229
00:10:15,400 --> 00:10:16,960
[Kim Sun Wook: so...]

230
00:10:17,760 --> 00:10:20,600
[Kim Sun Wook: I was curious about that chat.]

231
00:10:20,600 --> 00:10:22,920
[Kim Sun Wook:
It's my first Anonymous Chat after all,]

232
00:10:23,560 --> 00:10:24,960
[Kim Sun Wook: so I was curious.]

233
00:10:24,960 --> 00:10:27,680
[Kim Sun Wook: But I didn't go in in the end.]

