238
00:10:39,070 --> 00:10:40,790
[Lee Hyun Jun: I still feel very comfortable]

239
00:10:40,790 --> 00:10:42,670
[Lee Hyun Jun: around Han Gyeol.]

240
00:10:43,670 --> 00:10:47,510
