250
00:11:13,230 --> 00:11:15,030
[Lee Hyun Jun: The zoo itself was fun.]

251
00:11:15,030 --> 00:11:16,830
[Lee Hyun Jun: But since it was three of us,]

252
00:11:17,470 --> 00:11:19,750
