if there's anyone you're interested in.]

257
00:11:33,250 --> 00:11:34,890
[Lee Hyun Jun: There is.]

258
00:11:37,090 --> 00:11:39,730
[Lee Hyun Jun: Why do you ask?]
[Kim Sun Wook: I'm just curious.]

259
00:11:39,730 --> 00:11:41,850
[Kim Sun Wook: Who are you interested in?]

260
00:11:44,050 --> 00:11:45,770
[Lee Hyun Jun: That's a secret.]

261
