266
00:12:03,500 --> 00:12:05,970
[Lee Hyun Jun: As for the rest, it's a secret.]

267
00:12:08,210 --> 00:12:09,970
[Lee Hyun Jun: Why?]
[Kim Sun Wook: Just.]

268
00:12:09,970 --> 00:12:11,150
