I didn't think you'd say it's a secret.]

273
00:12:22,490 --> 00:12:24,970
[Lee Hyun Jun: I learned it somewhere.]

274
00:12:26,010 --> 00:12:27,970
[Lee Hyun Jun: Conversational back and forth?]

275
00:12:27,970 --> 00:12:30,450
[Lee Hyun Jun: We get along well like friends.]

276
00:12:30,770 --> 00:12:34,370
[Kim Sun Wook: He likes to joke,
even though he looks quiet.]

277
00:12:34,770 --> 00:12:39,930
[Kim Sun Wook: At times, he talks non-stop.]

278
00:12:42,450 --> 00:12:45,210
[Getting closer through their dinner for two]

279
