288
00:13:27,150 --> 00:13:28,390
[Kim Sun Wook: There's one left!]

289
00:13:36,270 --> 00:13:37,750
[Kim Sun Wook: It looks good.]

290
00:13:42,270 --> 00:13:43,430
[Kim Sun Wook: It looks good.]

291
00:13:43,430 --> 00:13:44,110
[Kim Sun Wook: I like this.]

292
00:13:44,110 --> 00:13:45,390
[Lee Hyun Jun: You do?]
[Kim Sun Wook: Yeah.]

293
00:13:45,670 --> 00:13:46,710
[Lee Hyun Jun: That's good.]

294
00:13:48,470 --> 00:13:51,150
[Lee Hyun Jun: I had fun
taking Four-Cut photos with him too.]

295
00:13:51,150 --> 00:13:53,150
[Lee Hyun Jun: I was happy that we got to spend]

296
00:13:53,150 --> 00:13:55,270
[Lee Hyun Jun: a lot of alone time together.]

297
00:13:55,750 --> 00:13:57,510
[Lee Hyun Jun: What do you think
of your first time on Nami Island?]

298
00:13:57,510 --> 00:13:59,630
[Kim Sun Wook:
I had a good time because it's with you.]

299
00:13:59,990 --> 00:14:02,670
[Kim Sun Wook: Nami Island was fun.]

300
00:14:02,670 --> 00:14:05,030
[Kim Sun Wook: Let's go to many more places.]
[(Nods)]

301
00:14:06,750 --> 00:14:09,030
[Kim Sun Wook: It became clear to me.]

302
00:14:09,310 --> 00:14:12,390
[Kim Sun Wook:
I'm gonna focus on Hyun Jun and go for it.]

303
00:14:12,710 --> 00:14:16,830
[Kim Sun Wook:
After our first date, I became sure.]

304
