How do you feel now that you're out?]

306
00:14:24,460 --> 00:14:27,620
[Cho Yun Jae: It's been a while. It's nice.]

307
00:14:28,220 --> 00:14:30,540
[Park Jae Ha: Hello.]

308
00:14:29,870 --> 00:14:30,620
Hello.

309
00:14:31,900 --> 00:14:35,140
[Park Jae Ha: Let's buy tickets first.]

310
