[Park Jae Ha: Didn't we agree to drop honorifics?]
[Cho Yun Jae: Right.]

315
00:14:55,860 --> 00:14:58,420
[Park Jae Ha: So let's talk casually?]
[Cho Yun Jae: OK.]

316
00:14:58,420 --> 00:14:59,460
[Park Jae Ha: Let's talk casually.]

317
00:15:00,020 --> 00:15:02,300
[Park Jae Ha: But I might
slip into honorifics from time to time.]

318
00:15:02,300 --> 00:15:04,060
