343
00:16:01,460 --> 00:16:03,310
[Cho Yun Jae: Oh, it's nice.]

344
00:16:05,430 --> 00:16:07,550
[Cho Yun Jae: Nice, nice. Want to see mine?]

345
00:16:08,230 --> 00:16:11,470
