but the photos I took might not be so good.]

346
00:16:13,900 --> 00:16:14,900
[Pfft]

347
00:16:14,900 --> 00:16:15,710
[What's wrong?]

348
00:16:15,830 --> 00:16:16,550
[Park Jae Ha: I like it.]

349
00:16:16,550 --> 00:16:18,030
[Cho Yun Jae: No, really.]

350
00:16:18,030 --> 00:16:19,150
[Park Jae Ha: You're good.]
[Cho Yun Jae: Isn't it nice?]

351
00:16:19,150 --> 00:16:21,390
[Park Jae Ha: You're good.]
[Cho Yun Jae: Seriously.]

352
00:16:21,390 --> 00:16:24,030
[Park Jae Ha: You're good.]
[Cho Yun Jae: Be serious!]

353
00:16:24,030 --> 00:16:26,270
[Park Jae Ha: You're good, seriously.]

354
00:16:27,390 --> 00:16:29,870
[Park Jae Ha: Want a chance to redeem yourself?]
[Cho Yun Jae: Yes.]

355
00:16:29,870 --> 00:16:31,310
[Park Jae Ha: OK. Redeem yourself.]

356
00:16:31,630 --> 00:16:33,990
[Cho Yun Jae: I'll try various angles now.]

357
00:16:34,710 --> 00:16:35,690
What should I do?

358
00:16:36,750 --> 00:16:39,150
[Park Jae Ha: I'll give you a tip. Use 2x zoom.]

359
00:16:41,670 --> 00:16:43,390
[Cho Yun Jae: I think I did good this time.]

360
00:16:44,630 --> 00:16:47,630
[Cho Yun Jae: This one's about the artsy vibes.]

361
00:16:47,630 --> 00:16:49,670
[Park Jae Ha: Too abstract for me.]

362
00:16:53,990 --> 00:16:57,550
[They get closer
as they capture each other through the lens]

363
00:17:03,790 --> 00:17:06,430
[Next, they have a chat in a cafe]

364
00:17:06,430 --> 00:17:08,510
[Park Jae Ha: You cut it well.]
[Cho Yun Jae: Yeah.]

365
00:17:08,510 --> 00:17:10,790
[Cho Yun Jae: I put my heart and soul into it.]

366
00:17:13,140 --> 00:17:14,060
[Content]

367
00:17:15,060 --> 00:17:16,540
[Satisfied]

368
00:17:17,060 --> 00:17:19,099
[Mm...]

369
00:17:20,390 --> 00:17:21,800
[Park Jae Ha: What's with your reaction?]

370
00:17:21,800 --> 00:17:22,710
[Cho Yun Jae: No.]

371
00:17:22,710 --> 00:17:25,430
[Cho Yun Jae: It's delicious.]

372
00:17:25,900 --> 00:17:27,950
[Park Jae Ha: How was this date?]

373
00:17:29,750 --> 00:17:34,150
[Cho Yun Jae: We haven't
had a chance to talk much before,]

374
00:17:34,150 --> 00:17:38,590
[Cho Yun Jae:
since we're not roommates and stuff.]

375
00:17:38,590 --> 00:17:43,750
[Cho Yun Jae: I think we had a good chat today.]

376
00:17:44,230 --> 00:17:48,190
[Cho Yun Jae: So we got closer.]

377
00:17:48,190 --> 00:17:50,990
[Park Jae Ha:
Is there anything you want to ask me?]

378
00:17:50,990 --> 00:17:53,790
[Cho Yun Jae: A... A lot.]
[Park Jae Ha: A lot?]

379
00:17:54,500 --> 00:18:00,510
[Cho Yun Jae: First, I'm curious
why you chose me for today's date.]

380
00:18:00,510 --> 00:18:02,110
[Park Jae Ha: Why I chose you?]

381
00:18:04,630 --> 00:18:10,030
[Park Jae Ha: First of all, I've been
feeling guilty about choosing you.]

382
00:18:10,030 --> 00:18:12,830
[Park Jae Ha: And grateful too, because, uh...]

383
00:18:11,630 --> 00:18:12,320
Guilty?

384
00:18:17,630 --> 00:18:21,110
[Park Jae Ha: To be honest, I didn't choose you
because I was interested in you.]

385
00:18:21,110 --> 00:18:23,070
[Park Jae Ha:
I just didn't want to stay in the dorm.]

386
00:18:23,070 --> 00:18:27,910
[Park Jae Ha: Since you've
expressed your interest in me,]

387
00:18:27,910 --> 00:18:31,390
[Park Jae Ha: I thought if I chose you,]

388
00:18:31,390 --> 00:18:35,550
[Park Jae Ha: I'd get to
go out for some fresh air.]

389
00:18:36,230 --> 00:18:38,190
[Park Jae Ha: After I
failed to match (with Hyeong Jun),]

390
00:18:38,710 --> 00:18:42,710
[Park Jae Ha: I was sad and down, and also angry.]

391
00:18:43,350 --> 00:18:46,070
[Park Jae Ha: When I received the text
that I could choose a date again,]

392
00:18:46,070 --> 00:18:48,150
[Park Jae Ha: I saw Yun Jae next to me.]

393
00:18:48,590 --> 00:18:53,630
[Park Jae Ha: So I debated between
choosing Yun Jae and staying at the dorm.]

394
00:18:53,910 --> 00:18:57,990
[Park Jae Ha: Since Hyeong Jun
didn't care about me at all,]

395
00:18:57,990 --> 00:19:01,470
[Park Jae Ha: and even ignored me,
in the heat of the moment,]

396
00:19:01,750 --> 00:19:05,590
[Park Jae Ha: I applied to
go on a date with Yun Jae.]

397
00:19:05,990 --> 00:19:08,190
[Jae Ha's bold and honest confession]

398
00:19:08,630 --> 00:19:10,550
[Park Jae Ha:
When we smoked together, we talked about]

399
00:19:10,950 --> 00:19:13,670
[Park Jae Ha: whether a couple was formed
in the previous shoot.]

400
00:19:13,910 --> 00:19:15,710
[Cho Yun Jae: Mm-hmm...]

401
00:19:16,310 --> 00:19:22,190
[Park Jae Ha: Back then,
Hyeong Jun and I became a couple,]

402
00:19:22,190 --> 00:19:25,910
[Park Jae Ha: and we began dating officially.]

403
00:19:26,710 --> 00:19:30,750
[Park Jae Ha: But as you know,]

404
00:19:31,470 --> 00:19:37,950
[Park Jae Ha: we had to reshoot
due to unforeseen circumstances.]

405
00:19:37,950 --> 00:19:40,990
[Park Jae Ha: In the process, Hyeong Jun and I]

406
00:19:41,470 --> 00:19:44,630
[Park Jae Ha: broke up.]

407
00:19:45,390 --> 00:19:49,950
[Jae Ha calmly reveals the backstory to Yun Jae]

408
00:19:49,950 --> 00:19:55,230
[Park Jae Ha: First, it'd be really
unfair to you and Han Gyeol]

409
00:19:55,230 --> 00:20:00,790
[Park Jae Ha: if there's all this tension
going on, as it'll disrupt you.]

410
00:20:00,790 --> 00:20:07,070
[Park Jae Ha: When the whole process is
already awkward and nerve-racking in itself.]

411
00:20:07,750 --> 00:20:09,270
[Park Jae Ha: I don't want]

412
00:20:09,270 --> 00:20:14,830
[Park Jae Ha: my situation
to affect everyone negatively.]

413
00:20:14,830 --> 00:20:17,190
[Park Jae Ha: I think it's very
inappropriate and rude.]

414
00:20:22,550 --> 00:20:26,230
[An overly honest confession by Jae Ha]

415
00:20:27,190 --> 00:20:31,230
[Park Jae Ha: I thought I should
tell him why I chose him for the date.]

416
00:20:31,550 --> 00:20:33,870
[Park Jae Ha: That's what fair and respectful.]

417
00:20:34,510 --> 00:20:38,070
[Park Jae Ha: I also wanted
to express my gratitude to him.]

418
00:20:38,950 --> 00:20:41,950
[Cho Yun Jae: But you really cleared my doubts.]

419
00:20:41,950 --> 00:20:45,340
[Cho Yun Jae: I understand you better now too.]

420
00:20:45,340 --> 00:20:48,890
[Cho Yun Jae: How should I put it?
It's a load off my mind.]

421
00:20:49,150 --> 00:20:50,500
[Park Jae Ha: How you feel?]
[Cho Yun Jae: Yeah.]

422
00:20:50,500 --> 00:20:53,380
[Park Jae Ha: That's a relief.]

423
00:20:53,380 --> 00:21:00,070
[Cho Yun Jae: He told me everything
that happened from the first shoot.]

424
00:21:00,070 --> 00:21:03,300
[Cho Yun Jae: We could organize our thoughts.]

425
00:21:03,590 --> 00:21:06,830
[I felt relieved.]

426
00:21:08,350 --> 00:21:10,970
[Park Jae Ha: I'll tell you
everything you want to know.]

427
00:21:10,990 --> 00:21:12,830
[Park Jae Ha: Anything else you want to know?]

428
00:21:13,630 --> 00:21:17,430
[Cho Yun Jae: Just tell me if it's true or not.
I might be mistaken.]

429
00:21:19,550 --> 00:21:22,660
[Cho Yun Jae: Was your chat nickname "GREEN"?]

430
00:21:23,400 --> 00:21:25,580
[Park Jae Ha: No, I wasn't GREEN.]

431
00:21:25,590 --> 00:21:27,730
[Cho Yun Jae: Really?]
[Park Jae Ha: Yeah, I wasn't.]

432
00:21:28,030 --> 00:21:29,760
[Cho Yun Jae: Really?]

433
00:21:31,670 --> 00:21:36,120
[Park Jae Ha: We both have bad intuition.]
[Cho Yun Jae: Since you said you were vegetarian.]

434
00:21:38,190 --> 00:21:41,260
[Cho Yun Jae: And you said you come up
with nicknames with what's in front of you,]

435
00:21:41,270 --> 00:21:46,010
[Cho Yun Jae: and you had
a green bottle of eye drops yesterday.]

436
00:21:46,010 --> 00:21:47,480
[Last night]

437
00:21:47,490 --> 00:21:50,880
[Park Jae Ha: I come up with nicknames
using what's in front of me,]

438
00:21:50,890 --> 00:21:53,380
[Park Jae Ha: even for gaming IDs.]

439
00:21:53,660 --> 00:21:55,500
[Green bottle of eye drops]

440
00:21:56,940 --> 00:21:59,570
[Yun Jae's well-founded misunderstanding]

441
00:21:59,690 --> 00:22:06,030
[Cho Yun Jae: So I thought
it might've been you. So it wasn't.]

442
00:22:06,430 --> 00:22:10,730
[Park Jae Ha: Did anyone wear green yesterday?]
[Cho Yun Jae: No.]

443
00:22:10,910 --> 00:22:13,990
[Cho Yun Jae:
I don't think it's that straightforward.]

444
00:22:14,430 --> 00:22:16,270
[Park Jae Ha: Do you
think a lot to come up with nicknames?]

445
00:22:16,290 --> 00:22:19,230
[Cho Yun Jae: No, I didn't think too much too.]

446
00:22:17,690 --> 00:22:18,560
Yeah. See?

447
00:22:20,430 --> 00:22:23,820
[Cho Yun Jae: One was GREEN, and the other...]

448
00:22:23,820 --> 00:22:28,220
[Cho Yun Jae: Was it BINGE-EATING CRONG?
Something similar anyway.]

449
00:22:31,440 --> 00:22:35,900
[I'm still curious who those two were...]

450
00:22:35,900 --> 00:22:39,120
[Cho Yun Jae: But it's likely
that CRONG was him, right?]

451
00:22:39,130 --> 00:22:41,700
[Park Jae Ha: I think CRONG was Hyun Jun.]
[Cho Yun Jae: I think so too.]

452
00:22:41,710 --> 00:22:44,830
[Park Jae Ha: That should be Hyun Jun.]

453
00:22:47,030 --> 00:22:50,840
[Cho Yun Jae: I need to confirm it
to properly organize my thoughts.]

454
00:22:51,210 --> 00:22:53,810
[Yun Jae needs definite answers]

455
00:22:54,950 --> 00:22:56,660
[Cho Yun Jae: To be honest,]

456
00:22:57,540 --> 00:22:59,340
[Cho Yun Jae: it matters a lot to me]

457
00:22:59,340 --> 00:23:03,540
[Cho Yun Jae:
whether Hyun Jun joined my chat or not.]

458
00:23:03,960 --> 00:23:07,780
[Cho Yun Jae: Because he
reciprocated my interest on the first day,]

459
00:23:07,800 --> 00:23:11,770
[Cho Yun Jae:
but I didn't receive a gift the next day.]

460
00:23:11,770 --> 00:23:14,220
[Cho Yun Jae:
It means he had a change of heart.]

461
00:23:14,230 --> 00:23:17,220
[Cho Yun Jae: I really want to know why.]

462
00:23:17,230 --> 00:23:19,190
[Cho Yun Jae: I can't stand not knowing stuff.]

463
00:23:19,190 --> 00:23:23,810
[Park Jae Ha: Has it been taxing on you?
Like emotionally draining?]

464
00:23:23,810 --> 00:23:25,370
[Cho Yun Jae: What I find tough is]

465
00:23:25,380 --> 00:23:31,050
[Cho Yun Jae:
now that I know he's interested in Sun Wook...]

466
00:23:31,410 --> 00:23:35,570
[Cho Yun Jae: I kinda sensed it yesterday.]
[Park Jae Ha: Really?]

467
00:23:35,880 --> 00:23:36,550
So...

468
00:23:36,690 --> 00:23:41,800
[Cho Yun Jae: But I've somewhat
gotten a bit closer with Sun Wook.]

469
00:23:42,110 --> 00:23:44,490
[Cho Yun Jae: That's what I find awkward.]

470
00:23:44,500 --> 00:23:46,230
[Park Jae Ha: Yes, it's inevitable.]

471
00:23:46,630 --> 00:23:50,020
[Park Jae Ha: Anyway, on the first day,
there was some reciprocation]

472
00:23:50,030 --> 00:23:52,610
[Park Jae Ha: between you and Hyun Jun.]

473
00:23:53,070 --> 00:23:58,790
[Cho Yun Jae: The more I think about why he
changed his mind, the more insecure I become.]

474
00:23:59,980 --> 00:24:02,900
[Park Jae Ha: Maybe Sun Wook
tried harder to pursue Hyun Jun than you.]

475
00:24:02,900 --> 00:24:03,950
[Cho Yun Jae: Right.]

476
00:24:03,970 --> 00:24:07,130
[Cho Yun Jae: When did he take action...]
[Park Jae Ha: You were careless.]

477
00:24:08,080 --> 00:24:12,660
[Cho Yun Jae: So people have been
making moves proactively and discreetly.]

478
00:24:12,660 --> 00:24:22,490
[Cho Yun Jae: I think my crush
was taken away because I was careless.]

479
00:24:23,190 --> 00:24:26,950
[Cho Yun Jae: I've been conflicted, debating on]

480
00:24:26,950 --> 00:24:31,100
[Cho Yun Jae:
whether to give up or to keep going.]

481
00:24:31,780 --> 00:24:34,480
[His clumsy feelings for Hyun Jun]

482
00:24:35,510 --> 00:24:39,490
[Cho Yun Jae: What do you think I should do
to get Hyun Jun's attention?]

483
00:24:40,180 --> 00:24:43,530
[Park Jae Ha: I think he's kind of oblivious too.]

484
00:24:43,530 --> 00:24:46,770
[Cho Yun Jae: No, he's really perceptive.]
[Park Jae Ha: Hyun Jun?]

485
00:24:47,100 --> 00:24:48,990
[Cho Yun Jae: He's lowkey very observant.]

486
00:24:50,050 --> 00:24:51,550
[Park Jae Ha: Really?]

487
00:24:51,570 --> 00:24:54,670
[Park Jae Ha: I think the most effective way
is to ask him directly.]

488
00:24:54,670 --> 00:24:56,370
[Park Jae Ha: Because the time]

489
00:24:56,370 --> 00:25:00,730
[Park Jae Ha: we have is very short.]

490
00:25:00,730 --> 00:25:02,560
[Park Jae Ha: If you don't ask, you won't know.]

491
00:25:03,190 --> 00:25:06,370
[Park Jae Ha: If he's determined
to hide his feelings, no one can tell.]

492
00:25:06,370 --> 00:25:10,490
[Park Jae Ha: The only way to know
is to ask him directly.]

493
00:25:10,990 --> 00:25:13,450
[Cho Yun Jae: I see...]

494
00:25:14,670 --> 00:25:19,700
[Cho Yun Jae: What did I do wrong?]
[Park Jae Ha: You did nothing wrong.]

495
00:25:18,930 --> 00:25:21,110
-Right? -You did nothing wrong.

496
00:25:23,260 --> 00:25:26,670
[A non-romantic but comforting time]

497
00:25:27,470 --> 00:25:30,870
[Jae Ha & Yun Jae's date comes to an end]

498
00:25:43,830 --> 00:25:46,100
[Kim Su Min: I'm a little bored.]

499
00:25:54,670 --> 00:25:58,680
[Lee Hyeok Jin: You are really calm.]
[Kim Su Min: Me?]

500
00:25:58,690 --> 00:26:01,730
[Lee Hyeok Jin: So totally calm.]

501
00:26:01,750 --> 00:26:04,910
[Kim Su Min: Have I always been this calm?]

502
00:26:10,030 --> 00:26:14,610
[Kim Su Min: Did you leave the lemonade upstairs?]
[Lee Hyeok Jin: It's a secret!]

503
00:26:14,610 --> 00:26:16,190
[Lee Hyeok Jin: I left it in the fridge.]

504
00:26:16,200 --> 00:26:23,480
[Lee Hyeok Jin: And I wrote a note.
I wrote his name on it.]

505
00:26:23,660 --> 00:26:25,930
[A while ago]

506
00:26:26,620 --> 00:26:28,220
[Lee Hyeok Jin: I went to Block A.]

507
00:26:28,220 --> 00:26:31,820
[Lee Hyeok Jin: I wrote "For Han Gyeol-hyung
who can't take caffeine" on the cup.]

508
00:26:31,820 --> 00:26:32,970
[Lee Hyeok Jin: And then...]

509
00:26:36,810 --> 00:26:42,140
[Hyeok Jin starts to make a move on Han Gyeol]

510
00:26:44,150 --> 00:26:45,830
[Lee Hyeok Jin: Hearing this,
have you figured out who my crush is?]

511
00:26:45,860 --> 00:26:48,870
[Kim Su Min: I'm not that oblivious.]

512
00:26:49,620 --> 00:26:58,820
[Yun Jae and Jae Ha have returned to Men's House]

513
00:26:58,830 --> 00:27:02,230
[Lee Hyeok Jin: Ha-hyung is here.]

514
00:27:02,910 --> 00:27:06,230
[Park Jae Ha: Heyo, heyo.
I heard you two went on a date.]

515
00:27:06,230 --> 00:27:08,860
[Kim Su Min: Yes, we did.]

516
00:27:08,880 --> 00:27:11,550
[Kim Su Min: What did you do?]

517
00:27:11,550 --> 00:27:16,580
[Park Jae Ha: Just... Looked around, and talked.]

518
00:27:16,580 --> 00:27:20,350
[Park Jae Ha: I told him about Hyeong Jun and I,]

519
00:27:20,350 --> 00:27:26,080
[Park Jae Ha: and what happened before.
I apologized too.]

520
00:27:26,080 --> 00:27:29,710
[Park Jae Ha: But Yun jae also chose me
because of a misunderstanding.]

521
00:27:29,710 --> 00:27:31,340
[Kim Su Min: What misunderstanding?]

522
00:27:31,340 --> 00:27:35,380
[Park Jae Ha: Two people
joined his Anonymous Chat.]

523
00:27:35,390 --> 00:27:39,570
[Park Jae Ha: He thought I was one of them.]

524
00:27:41,550 --> 00:27:42,940
[Lee Hyeok Jin: Who is it?]

525
00:27:42,940 --> 00:27:44,460
[Cho Yun Jae: Guess who I am.]

526
00:27:44,460 --> 00:27:47,060
[Yun Jae]

527
00:27:44,540 --> 00:27:45,600
-Yun Jae. -Yun Jae.

528
00:27:47,840 --> 00:27:51,150
[Cho Yun Jae: You know who GREEN is, right?]
[Lee Hyeok Jin: Yes.]

529
00:27:51,160 --> 00:27:53,260
[Park Jae Ha: You do?]
[Lee Hyeok Jin: It was me.]

530
00:27:53,270 --> 00:27:55,110
[Park Jae Ha: It was you? Seriously?]

531
00:27:55,440 --> 00:27:59,010
[Cho Yun Jae: He... He's lying.]

532
00:27:58,110 --> 00:27:59,320
He's a good liar.

533
00:27:59,030 --> 00:28:00,510
[Cho Yun Jae: He's always bluffing.]

534
00:28:01,220 --> 00:28:03,380
[Lee Hyeok Jin: Have you been making moves?]

535
00:28:03,400 --> 00:28:05,900
[Cho Yun Jae: No.]
[Lee Hyeok Jin: Why not?]

536
00:28:06,190 --> 00:28:09,020
[Cho Yun Jae: I don't know what to do.]
[Park Jae Ha: He lacks courage.]

537
00:28:08,480 --> 00:28:09,270
Not enough courage.

538
00:28:09,020 --> 00:28:11,190
[Lee Hyeok Jin: Why? Is it because]

539
00:28:11,190 --> 00:28:14,040
[Lee Hyeok Jin: you can tell that
other people are interested in him?]

540
00:28:14,040 --> 00:28:17,910
[Cho Yun Jae: Before that, I was too complacent.]

541
00:28:17,910 --> 00:28:19,660
[Cho Yun Jae: I didn't take any action.]

542
00:28:19,660 --> 00:28:21,880
[Cho Yun Jae: But now that there's someone else,]

543
00:28:21,880 --> 00:28:23,980
[Cho Yun Jae: I'm so bothered by it
that I can't do anything.]

544
00:28:23,990 --> 00:28:24,690
[Lee Hyeok Jin: Even worse]

545
00:28:24,700 --> 00:28:27,060
[Lee Hyeok Jin: with all the missions, right?]
[Cho Yun Jae: Yeah.]

546
00:28:27,060 --> 00:28:29,780
[Lee Hyeok Jin: Makes it feel like
we have to do something.]

547
00:28:29,820 --> 00:28:32,180
[A glance]

548
00:28:32,260 --> 00:28:34,760
[Lee Hyeok Jin:
It's more stressful than expected.]

549
00:28:33,530 --> 00:28:34,460
This situation.

550
00:28:34,760 --> 00:28:40,050
[Cho Yun Jae: So I'm gonna change starting today.]
[Lee Hyeok Jin: Good, that's the spirit.]

551
00:28:40,060 --> 00:28:42,740
[Lee Hyeok Jin: I think
I know who you're interested in.]

552
00:28:42,740 --> 00:28:45,820
[Cho Yun Jae: It's stranger if you don't know.]

553
00:28:45,820 --> 00:28:49,180
[Cho Yun Jae: It's been
the same person for me since Day One.]

554
00:28:49,200 --> 00:28:51,270
[Lee Hyeok Jin: Can I say it?]
[Cho Yun Jae: Yeah.]

555
00:28:51,270 --> 00:28:53,870
[Lee Hyeok Jin: Hyun Jun?]
[Cho Yun Jae: Yeah.]

556
00:28:56,010 --> 00:29:00,700
[Lee Hyeok Jin: Go for it.]
[Cho Yun Jae: I want to.]

557
00:29:00,700 --> 00:29:06,740
[Cho Yun Jae: I really want to just go for it.]
[Lee Hyeok Jin: It's so hard, really hard.]

558
00:29:06,740 --> 00:29:11,980
[Cho Yun Jae: Someone else
suddenly came into the picture.]

559
00:29:11,980 --> 00:29:16,220
[A glance] [A glance]

560
00:29:17,100 --> 00:29:18,700
[Lee Hyeok Jin: Is someone coming?]

561
00:29:18,710 --> 00:29:21,560
[Park Jae Ha: Always on the lookout for his prey.]
[Lee Hyeok Jin: Right?]

562
00:29:21,560 --> 00:29:23,220
[Lee Hyeok Jin: I wonder who he's waiting for.]

563
00:29:23,220 --> 00:29:26,710
[Park Jae Ha: Someone is coming up again.
Look carefully. Who is it?]

564
00:29:25,150 --> 00:29:25,810
Really?

565
00:29:27,060 --> 00:29:30,110
[Who is the one climbing up the slope?]

566
00:29:27,990 --> 00:29:30,030
Someone's here.

567
00:29:35,660 --> 00:29:38,100
[Staring]

568
00:29:38,480 --> 00:29:40,830
[Kim Han Gyeol: Where are you going?
What are you doing?]

569
00:29:40,830 --> 00:29:43,190
[Lee Hyeok Jin: Did you have a good time?]

570
00:29:43,200 --> 00:29:46,640
[Hyeok Jin was waiting for Han Gyeol]

571
00:29:43,780 --> 00:29:45,220
-How was it? -It was fun.

572
00:29:46,640 --> 00:29:49,580
[Lee Hyeok Jin: Did you have a good chat?]
[Kim Han Gyeol: There wasn't much time to talk.]

573
00:29:49,580 --> 00:29:52,380
[Lee Hyeok Jin: Oh, too busy exercising?]
[Kim Han Gyeol: Yeah.]

574
00:29:52,380 --> 00:29:55,420
[Lee Hyeok Jin: What? Just like yesterday?]
[Kim Han Gyeol: Yeah.]

575
00:29:56,150 --> 00:30:01,280
[Lee Hyeok Jin: Hyung, here, in this fridge,]

576
00:30:01,780 --> 00:30:03,820
[Lee Hyeok Jin: I left a cup of lemon tea.]

577
00:30:03,820 --> 00:30:07,240
[Lee Hyeok Jin: It's for you. No caffeine.]

578
00:30:07,240 --> 00:30:10,500
[Lee Hyeok Jin: Since you can't take caffeine.]

579
00:30:10,500 --> 00:30:12,970
[Lee Hyeok Jin: I bought it
when I bought my coffee.]

580
00:30:12,970 --> 00:30:14,450
[Kim Han Gyeol: Thank you.]

581
00:30:14,450 --> 00:30:17,880
[Lee Hyeok Jin: Drink it later.]
[Kim Han Gyeol: OK.]

582
00:30:17,900 --> 00:30:20,030
[Lee Hyeok Jin: I'm going to Block C.]

583
00:30:20,040 --> 00:30:21,180
[Kim Han Gyeol: Is everyone there?]
[Lee Hyeok Jin: Yeah.]

584
00:30:21,180 --> 00:30:23,620
[Kim Han Gyeol: I'll go there
after I sort this out.]

585
00:30:25,710 --> 00:30:28,350
[Lee Hyeok Jin: It went quite well. Also,]

586
00:30:28,360 --> 00:30:32,930
[Lee Hyeok Jin: I wrote his name
because I didn't want him to misunderstand.]

587
00:30:32,930 --> 00:30:35,900
[Lee Hyeok Jin: Eum Hyeok Jin also bought coffee]

588
00:30:36,320 --> 00:30:39,790
[Lee Hyeok Jin: from the same cafe.]

589
00:30:39,790 --> 00:30:41,720
[Lee Hyeok Jin: If he sees
Hyeok Jin drinking coffee,]

590
00:30:41,720 --> 00:30:46,220
[Lee Hyeok Jin: he might be confused as to]

591
00:30:46,220 --> 00:30:48,790
[Lee Hyeok Jin:
whether it was me or Eum Hyeok Jin]

592
00:30:48,800 --> 00:30:51,300
[Lee Hyeok Jin: who bought him the drink.
So to let him know]

593
00:30:51,610 --> 00:30:55,920
[Lee Hyeok Jin: (it was from someone younger
than him), I added a "hyung" behind his name.]

594
00:30:59,630 --> 00:31:04,040
[Taichi collapses onto the sofa]

595
00:31:06,060 --> 00:31:08,300
[A glance]

596
00:31:09,410 --> 00:31:12,660
[Taichi looks tired,]

597
00:31:12,660 --> 00:31:18,720
[so Han Gyeol turns around and leaves]

598
00:31:19,320 --> 00:31:20,320
I got goose bumps.

599
00:31:22,250 --> 00:31:24,540
[Kim Su Min: Hello.]
[Lee Hyeok Jin: Hello.]

600
00:31:24,540 --> 00:31:28,340
[Cho Yun Jae: Is Hyun Jun back?]
[Kim Han Gyeol: He just arrived. He's upstairs.]

601
00:31:28,340 --> 00:31:30,460
[Cho Yun Jae: Really?]

602
00:31:30,460 --> 00:31:34,240
[Cho Yun Jae: Glad you came.]

603
00:31:34,260 --> 00:31:37,100
[Lee Hyeok Jin: What is this?]

604
00:31:37,100 --> 00:31:40,680
[Kim Han Gyeol: We did yoga.]
[Kim Su Min: Yoga? How was it?]

605
00:31:40,700 --> 00:31:43,370
[Kim Han Gyeol: Very tiring.]
[Kim Su Min: Yeah?]

606
00:31:43,370 --> 00:31:47,530
[Kim Han Gyeol: We did splits
while holding hands and meditated.]

607
00:31:47,530 --> 00:31:50,000
[Kim Su Min: You went out with Taichi, right?]

608
00:31:50,000 --> 00:31:52,660
[Kim Han Gyeol: Ichi collapsed
as soon as he got back.]

609
00:31:52,670 --> 00:31:53,890
[Lee Hyeok Jin: When he has a cold.]

610
00:31:53,900 --> 00:31:56,940
[Kim Han Gyeol: Yeah, what luck
to do something intense while sick.]

611
00:31:56,940 --> 00:31:59,340
[Kim Su Min: Couples yoga
means doing it as partners?]

612
00:31:59,340 --> 00:32:01,740
[Kim Han Gyeol: Yeah, a lot of physical contact.]

613
00:32:01,740 --> 00:32:07,820
[Kim Han Gyeol: After the date...
I'm even more conflicted.]

614
00:32:08,300 --> 00:32:11,860
[Kim Su Min: I'll leave you two to talk.]

615
00:32:09,440 --> 00:32:11,110
-OK. -OK.

616
00:32:20,240 --> 00:32:22,220
[Lee Hyeok Jin:
Wear these slippers. Keep your feet warm.]

617
00:32:22,220 --> 00:32:24,210
[Kim Han Gyeol: Wow.]

618
00:32:24,210 --> 00:32:26,210
[Kim Han Gyeol: Everyone has nice slippers.]

619
00:32:26,210 --> 00:32:30,360
[Lee Hyeok Jin: I brought them.]
[Kim Han Gyeol: Oh, amazing. So spongy.]

620
00:32:30,370 --> 00:32:32,490
[Lee Hyeok Jin: Spongy, right?]

621
00:32:32,490 --> 00:32:36,320
[Lee Hyeok Jin: And the color's nice.
That's why I bought it. I like blue.]

622
00:32:36,330 --> 00:32:37,970
[Kim Han Gyeol: Oh, me too.]

623
00:32:37,970 --> 00:32:39,850
[Lee Hyeok Jin: Really?]

624
00:32:39,850 --> 00:32:43,830
[Kim Han Gyeol:
I like colors like blue and green.]

625
00:32:42,400 --> 00:32:43,090
I see.

626
00:32:44,490 --> 00:32:47,130
[Lee Hyeok Jin: So how was the date?]

627
00:32:47,130 --> 00:32:50,750
[Lee Hyeok Jin: How was it?
It was your first proper date.]

628
00:32:50,760 --> 00:32:55,400
[Kim Han Gyeol: He's sick,
so he's been sleeping a lot.]

629
00:32:55,400 --> 00:32:59,650
[Kim Han Gyeol: He's not feeling well either,
so we didn't talk much.]

630
00:32:59,650 --> 00:33:03,010
[Kim Han Gyeol:
After the date, I sensed something.]

631
00:33:05,330 --> 00:33:08,210
[Kim Han Gyeol: I wanted to ask him
to clarify, so I went upstairs.]

632
00:33:08,210 --> 00:33:10,860
[Kim Han Gyeol: But he collapsed onto the sofa
as soon as he got back.]

633
00:33:10,870 --> 00:33:14,480
[Kim Han Gyeol: So I just came here.]

634
00:33:14,490 --> 00:33:18,210
[Lee Hyeok Jin: You're all pouty now.]
[Kim Han Gyeol: Am I?]

635
00:33:18,210 --> 00:33:21,170
[Kim Han Gyeol: I'm just frustrated.]
[Lee Hyeok Jin: Yeah?]

636
00:33:21,760 --> 00:33:24,850
[Lee Hyeok Jin: Is it a positive change
or a negative change?]

637
00:33:24,850 --> 00:33:28,370
[Kim Han Gyeol: I need to
hear his answer first. I'll ask him]

638
00:33:28,370 --> 00:33:34,310
[Kim Han Gyeol: when he wakes up.
I want to hear his answer.]

639
00:33:34,620 --> 00:33:40,790
[Kim Han Gyeol: It's like he has no feelings
for me at all. Or am I overthinking it?]

640
00:33:41,250 --> 00:33:46,850
[Kim Han Gyeol: Is he just not expressive?
I have no idea.]

641
00:33:47,690 --> 00:33:52,470
[Kim Han Gyeol: Besides me,
is there anyone else you're interested in?]

642
00:33:57,290 --> 00:33:59,860
[Lee Hyeok Jin: There was.]

643
00:33:59,860 --> 00:34:05,930
[Lee Hyeok Jin:
But I'm more curious about you now.]

644
00:34:05,930 --> 00:34:08,510
[Lee Hyeok Jin: Did you think
I wasn't interested in you?]

645
00:34:08,510 --> 00:34:11,100
[Kim Han Gyeol: No, I didn't think that.]

646
00:34:11,100 --> 00:34:17,150
[Lee Hyeok Jin: That's a relief. Since you
said you wanted to know more about me,]

647
00:34:21,090 --> 00:34:27,770
[Lee Hyeok Jin: I thought maybe
you felt that I had no feelings for you.]

648
00:34:27,790 --> 00:34:31,440
[Lee Hyeok Jin: Right now,
I'm most curious about you.]

649
00:34:31,449 --> 00:34:36,949
[Lee Hyeok Jin: If I get to
go on a proper long date with you,]

650
00:34:36,960 --> 00:34:43,830
[Lee Hyeok Jin: I think
I'll get to know more about you.]

651
00:34:44,210 --> 00:34:47,770
[Kim Han Gyeol: You and Eum Hyeok Jin
have different styles.]

652
00:34:47,770 --> 00:34:51,330
[Lee Hyeok Jin: As in how we approach you?]

653
00:34:49,280 --> 00:34:49,900
Yeah.

654
00:34:51,940 --> 00:34:55,310
[Lee Hyeok Jin: I'm gonna do my best.]

655
00:34:55,320 --> 00:34:58,020
[Lee Hyeok Jin:
I want to go on a more serious date.]

656
00:34:58,020 --> 00:35:02,960
[Lee Hyeok Jin: On the first day,
it was just getting to know each other]

657
00:35:02,970 --> 00:35:05,640
[Lee Hyeok Jin: based on first impressions.]

658
00:35:05,640 --> 00:35:08,390
[Lee Hyeok Jin: The second date was a trio date]

659
00:35:08,390 --> 00:35:11,710
[Lee Hyeok Jin: which wasn't romantic;
just a friends' outing.]

660
00:35:11,710 --> 00:35:13,870
[Lee Hyeok Jin:
So I really want to have a proper date.]

661
00:35:13,870 --> 00:35:16,190
[Lee Hyeok Jin: Why don't I get to]

662
00:35:16,190 --> 00:35:18,670
[Lee Hyeok Jin: go on a proper date]

663
00:35:18,670 --> 00:35:20,470
[Lee Hyeok Jin: with my crush?]

664
00:35:20,470 --> 00:35:23,710
[Lee Hyeok Jin:
I also want to go on casual walks with him.]

665
00:35:27,150 --> 00:35:34,030
[Lee Hyeok Jin: A lot on your mind, huh?]
[Kim Han Gyeol: Yeah, since yesterday.]

666
00:35:34,030 --> 00:35:36,870
[Lee Hyeok Jin: What's troubling you the most?]

667
00:35:37,390 --> 00:35:40,910
[Kim Han Gyeol: Him. I want to hear his answer.]

668
00:35:40,910 --> 00:35:47,670
[Lee Hyeok Jin: I see. Will it change things?]
[Kim Han Gyeol: Yes.]

669
00:35:47,670 --> 00:35:51,710
[Kim Han Gyeol: I'm so confused right now.]

670
00:35:51,710 --> 00:35:53,630
[Kim Han Gyeol: Total chaos.]

671
00:35:53,630 --> 00:35:58,030
[Kim Han Gyeol:
I need to sort it out before it's late.]

672
00:35:58,030 --> 00:36:01,030
[Kim Han Gyeol: Or it'll just come to nothing.]

673
00:36:03,350 --> 00:36:05,660
[Lee Hyeok Jin: Are you interested in me at all?]

674
00:36:05,660 --> 00:36:06,010
[In you?]

675
00:36:06,010 --> 00:36:06,330
[Yeah.]

676
00:36:06,330 --> 00:36:07,610
[Yeah.]
[I see.]

677
00:36:07,610 --> 00:36:10,590
[Kim Han Gyeol: Of course I am.]

678
00:36:10,610 --> 00:36:13,610
[Kim Han Gyeol: Of course I like it.
They're expressing their interest in me honestly.]

679
00:36:13,610 --> 00:36:18,050
[Kim Han Gyeol: Before the date with Taichi,
I had two dates with Hyeok Jin.]

680
00:36:18,050 --> 00:36:19,810
[Kim Han Gyeol: Now that
I've had a date with Taichi,]

681
00:36:19,810 --> 00:36:23,910
[Kim Han Gyeol: both Hyeok Jins
have been proactively approaching me.]

682
00:36:23,910 --> 00:36:27,270
[Kim Han Gyeol:
Because I was most drawn to Taichi at first,]

683
00:36:27,270 --> 00:36:29,750
[Kim Han Gyeol:
I thought the attraction would get stronger.]

684
00:36:29,750 --> 00:36:32,070
[Kim Han Gyeol: But it's stayed the same, so...]

685
00:36:32,790 --> 00:36:34,000
[Kim Han Gyeol: Where are you going?]

686
00:36:34,000 --> 00:36:35,990
[Taichi: I don't know.
Everyone went down, so I'm going too.]

687
00:36:35,990 --> 00:36:39,510
[Kim Han Gyeol: Oh, um, can we talk?]
[Taichi: Yeah.]

688
00:36:40,950 --> 00:36:44,710
[The time Han Gyeol has been waiting for]

689
00:36:45,750 --> 00:36:49,430
[Taichi: What's up?]
[Kim Han Gyeol: Uh...]

690
00:36:51,290 --> 00:36:52,040
What?

691
00:36:53,070 --> 00:36:58,710
[Kim Han Gyeol: Anyway, from the beginning,
since I chose you as my roommate,]

692
00:36:58,710 --> 00:37:01,630
[Kim Han Gyeol:
I've been expressing my interest in you.]

693
00:37:01,630 --> 00:37:06,270
[Kim Han Gyeol: So I...
Because I wanted to be honest with you.]

694
00:37:06,270 --> 00:37:11,750
[Kim Han Gyeol: But I feel like it's one-sided.
Do you find it burdensome?]

695
00:37:11,750 --> 00:37:15,390
[Taichi: It's not burdensome, but...]

696
00:37:15,390 --> 00:37:18,070
[Taichi: To be honest, I'm usually]

697
00:37:18,070 --> 00:37:24,830
[Taichi: the one who likes the other first
and makes one-sided advances.]

698
00:37:24,830 --> 00:37:26,790
[Taichi: It's not burdensome,]

699
00:37:26,790 --> 00:37:28,910
[Taichi: but I'm a bit unsure about]

700
00:37:28,910 --> 00:37:32,470
[Taichi: how I should respond to you.]

701
00:37:32,470 --> 00:37:36,030
[Taichi: I've been acting awkward.
So I'm sorry about that too.]

702
00:37:36,030 --> 00:37:37,830
[Taichi: But among everyone here,]

703
00:37:37,830 --> 00:37:40,430
[Taichi: I'm most interested to get to know you.]

704
00:37:40,430 --> 00:37:44,150
[Taichi: That's why I chose you for today's date.]

705
00:37:44,150 --> 00:37:45,990
[Taichi: Anyway, it's a pity that]

706
00:37:45,990 --> 00:37:49,350
[Taichi: we didn't get to talk much today.]

707
00:37:49,350 --> 00:37:51,230
[Taichi: I'd have preferred a date like that.]

708
00:37:50,310 --> 00:37:51,090
Me too.

709
00:37:51,950 --> 00:37:53,830
[Taichi: It's also my first time trying yoga.]

710
00:37:53,830 --> 00:37:56,990
[Taichi: There was no time to talk.]

711
00:37:56,990 --> 00:37:59,950
[Taichi: That was a pity, so]

712
00:37:59,950 --> 00:38:02,190
[Taichi: next time... I still think]

713
00:38:02,190 --> 00:38:04,790
[Taichi: I don't know you very well.]

714
00:38:04,790 --> 00:38:06,910
[Taichi: It's nice to talk in the room like this,]

715
00:38:06,910 --> 00:38:10,310
[Taichi: but I think I'd get to really know you]

716
00:38:10,310 --> 00:38:12,970
[Taichi: when we have a proper chat
on a date outside.]

717
00:38:13,490 --> 00:38:15,750
[Taichi: For you and for me.]

718
00:38:15,750 --> 00:38:17,230
[Taichi: So, honestly,]

719
00:38:17,230 --> 00:38:20,510
[Taichi: I still want to date with you next time.]

720
00:38:20,930 --> 00:38:24,390
[Kim Han Gyeol: Because our date just now]

721
00:38:24,390 --> 00:38:25,910
[Kim Han Gyeol: was an active date.]

722
00:38:26,490 --> 00:38:30,550
[Kim Han Gyeol: I know you're not feeling well,]

723
00:38:30,550 --> 00:38:32,430
[Kim Han Gyeol: so we didn't talk much.]

724
00:38:32,430 --> 00:38:36,550
[Kim Han Gyeol: To be honest,
I was really looking forward to our date.]

725
00:38:36,550 --> 00:38:40,390
[Kim Han Gyeol:
Since it was our first 1-on-1 date,]

726
00:38:40,390 --> 00:38:43,990
[Kim Han Gyeol: and I wanted to
have a proper chat with you, but I couldn't.]

727
00:38:43,990 --> 00:38:51,270
[Kim Han Gyeol: So I'm quite upset, personally.]
[Taichi: It was a bummer for me too.]

728
00:38:51,270 --> 00:38:55,510
[Taichi: And about changing rooms too.]

729
00:38:55,510 --> 00:38:56,910
[Taichi: It was bad timing too,]

730
00:38:56,910 --> 00:38:59,550
[Taichi: at a time when I'm also sick.]

731
00:38:58,910 --> 00:38:59,500
Yeah.

732
00:38:59,550 --> 00:39:02,550
[Taichi: So we didn't get to talk properly too.]

733
00:39:02,550 --> 00:39:05,350
[Taichi: And then you left.
I don't find you burdensome,]

734
00:39:05,350 --> 00:39:08,830
[Taichi: but I just don't know how to treat you.]

735
00:39:08,830 --> 00:39:11,950
[Taichi:
If that made you worried or sad, I'm sorry.]

736
00:39:11,950 --> 00:39:16,030
[Taichi: I want to
go on another date with you again.]

737
00:39:16,030 --> 00:39:18,990
[Taichi: I want to have a good chat]

738
00:39:18,990 --> 00:39:21,430
[Taichi: over a meal and stuff.]

739
00:39:21,430 --> 00:39:22,790
[Kim Han Gyeol: I think]

740
00:39:22,790 --> 00:39:25,230
[Kim Han Gyeol: I wanted to
hear you tell me what you thought,]

741
00:39:25,230 --> 00:39:27,550
[Kim Han Gyeol: whatever it was.]

742
00:39:27,870 --> 00:39:33,150
[Taichi: I'm being honest
with you right now. This is what I feel.]

743
00:39:33,150 --> 00:39:38,070
[Taichi: I'm most interested
in getting to know you.]

744
00:39:38,070 --> 00:39:40,870
[Taichi: It's just a lot of bad timing.]

745
00:39:39,290 --> 00:39:40,390
Yeah.

746
00:39:40,870 --> 00:39:44,430
[Taichi: So it's a bit...]
[Kim Han Gyeol: So I'm very frustrated.]

747
00:39:47,330 --> 00:39:49,490
[Kim Han Gyeol:
Let's go on another date next time.]

748
00:39:49,490 --> 00:39:53,970
[Taichi: Hope we can have a deep chat next time.]

749
00:39:53,970 --> 00:39:56,690
[Taichi: That would be great.]

750
00:39:58,430 --> 00:40:01,510
[Taichi: To be honest, it's a bit burdensome.]

751
00:40:01,510 --> 00:40:04,550
[Taichi: Although I said it wasn't burdensome,]

752
00:40:04,550 --> 00:40:08,150
[Taichi: I do find it a bit burdensome.
That's why I said all that.]

753
00:40:08,150 --> 00:40:10,590
[Taichi: Thinking from another standpoint,]

754
00:40:10,590 --> 00:40:11,870
[Taichi: if I'm attracted to him,]

755
00:40:11,870 --> 00:40:15,510
[Taichi: I wouldn't have said what I said to him.]

756
00:40:15,510 --> 00:40:17,830
[Taichi: It'd have all sounded like excuses.]

757
00:40:17,830 --> 00:40:22,350
[Taichi: I also feel bad for saying all that I'd said]

758
00:40:22,350 --> 00:40:24,190
[Taichi: and for feeling this way.]

759
00:40:26,270 --> 00:40:29,350
[I'm getting more and more conflicted...]

760
00:40:30,550 --> 00:40:34,350
[Rather than excitement,
a night filled with guilt and frustration]

761
00:40:35,450 --> 00:40:37,270
Where is everyone? In Block C?

762
00:40:35,790 --> 00:40:38,750
[Hyun Jun and Sun Wook
have returned to Men's House]

763
00:40:44,670 --> 00:40:48,070
[Taichi: What is this?]

764
00:40:48,070 --> 00:40:51,510
[Kim Sun Wook: You're back.]
[Taichi: Yeah.]

765
00:40:51,510 --> 00:40:54,510
[Taichi: What did you do?]
[Kim Sun Wook: You were sleeping like that.]

766
00:40:54,510 --> 00:40:57,310
[Lee Hyun Jun: Your sleeping posture is flexible.]
[Kim Sun Wook: We went to Nami Island.]

767
00:40:57,310 --> 00:41:01,670
[Taichi: We did yoga, so I got more flexible.]
[Kim Sun Wook: Oh, is that so?]

768
00:41:01,670 --> 00:41:03,750
[Lee Hyun Jun: Doesn't look like it.]

769
00:41:10,670 --> 00:41:14,750
[Yun Jae is heading towards Hyun Jun]

770
00:41:35,810 --> 00:41:38,090
It can't be helped. It'll be obvious.

771
00:41:37,070 --> 00:41:42,110
[The three seem to be
having an enjoyable conversation]

772
00:41:40,890 --> 00:41:42,090
I bet everyone knows.

773
00:41:43,650 --> 00:41:46,910
[Yun Jae turns around and leaves]

774
00:42:07,970 --> 00:42:12,250
[Motivation and energy down in no time]

775
00:42:13,240 --> 00:42:13,950
Yeah?

776
00:42:14,010 --> 00:42:19,850
[Hyun Jun has zero clue about Yun Jae's state]

777
00:42:15,040 --> 00:42:16,230
I think so too.

778
00:42:19,850 --> 00:42:21,630
[Park Jae Ha: Why do you look so empty?]

779
00:42:21,630 --> 00:42:24,430
[Kim Su Min: Hmm?]
[Park Jae Ha: Why do you look so out of it?]

780
00:42:24,430 --> 00:42:28,910
[Park Jae Ha:
Because things aren't going your way?]

781
00:42:31,110 --> 00:42:33,630
[Kim Su Min: It's my lack of confidence.]

782
00:42:33,630 --> 00:42:39,070
[Kim Su Min: About the guys I'm interested in]

783
00:42:39,070 --> 00:42:43,110
[Kim Su Min:
and the people they are attracted to.]

784
00:42:43,110 --> 00:42:45,910
[Kim Su Min: The guys I like always seem to]

785
00:42:45,910 --> 00:42:49,830
[Kim Su Min: be attracted to guys unlike me.]

786
00:42:50,110 --> 00:42:55,030
[Kim Su Min: In here, it's still the same.]

787
00:42:55,030 --> 00:42:58,030
[Kim Su Min:
So it's eating away at my confidence.]

788
00:42:58,030 --> 00:43:04,470
[Kim Su Min: I keep thinking
it won't work out no matter what I do,]

789
00:43:04,470 --> 00:43:07,250
[Kim Su Min: so I'm where I am now.]

790
00:43:07,670 --> 00:43:11,550
[Kim Su Min: I barely have any confidence now.]
[Park Jae Ha: Don't think that way.]

791
00:43:11,750 --> 00:43:13,830
[Park Jae Ha: Cheer up.]

792
00:43:14,670 --> 00:43:16,950
[Kim Su Min: Hyeong Jun is here.]

793
00:43:18,550 --> 00:43:22,310
[Park Jae Ha: I've been waiting
for Hyeong Jun to return after my date ended.]

794
00:43:22,310 --> 00:43:24,950
[Park Jae Ha: I have to go talk to him often]

795
00:43:24,950 --> 00:43:29,390
[Park Jae Ha: and express my
feelings and interest in him]

796
00:43:29,390 --> 00:43:32,630
[Park Jae Ha:
so that the week doesn't goes to waste.]

797
00:43:32,630 --> 00:43:35,870
[Park Jae Ha: So I've been
waiting for Hyeong Jun to come back.]

798
00:43:35,870 --> 00:43:38,790
[Park Jae Ha: I was waiting
for Hyeong Jun to pass by,]

799
00:43:38,790 --> 00:43:41,950
[Park Jae Ha: but I didn't see him,
so I went to wait]

800
00:43:41,950 --> 00:43:44,670
[Park Jae Ha: in his block.]

801
00:43:45,670 --> 00:43:48,830
[The long-awaited Hyeong Jun appears]

802
00:43:50,850 --> 00:43:53,590
[Jae Ha reacts to it right away]

803
00:44:00,590 --> 00:44:03,550
[Park Jae Ha: You're back.]
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Yeah.]

804
00:44:05,310 --> 00:44:08,950
[Kim Su Min: Hi.]
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Hello.]

805
00:44:18,190 --> 00:44:20,990
[Park Jae Ha: It's so dark.]

806
00:44:34,870 --> 00:44:37,660
[Park Jae Ha: Are you cleaning up?]
[Lee Hyeong Jun: No.]

807
00:44:39,490 --> 00:44:41,490
[Startled]

808
00:44:46,300 --> 00:44:50,120
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Why are you standing there?]

809
00:44:50,120 --> 00:44:55,640
[Park Jae Ha: Hmm? I'm curious about your date.]
[Lee Hyeong Jun: What for?]

810
00:44:55,640 --> 00:45:02,260
[Park Jae Ha: Aren't you curious about my date?]
[Lee Hyeong Jun: No, not really.]

811
00:45:02,260 --> 00:45:04,560
[Park Jae Ha: Really?]
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Yeah.]

812
00:45:04,560 --> 00:45:07,640
[Park Jae Ha: I told Yun Jae]

813
00:45:07,640 --> 00:45:10,560
[Park Jae Ha: about you and me,]

814
00:45:10,560 --> 00:45:12,920
[Park Jae Ha: and that I only chose him
because I wanted to go out]

815
00:45:12,920 --> 00:45:14,840
[Park Jae Ha: and apologized to him.]

816
00:45:14,840 --> 00:45:19,000
[Park Jae Ha:
I told him I'm not interested in him.]

817
00:45:19,000 --> 00:45:24,960
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Why are you telling me this?]
[Park Jae Ha: I want to reconcile with you.]

818
00:45:33,000 --> 00:45:38,600
[Park Jae Ha: Want some water?]
[Lee Hyeong Jun: I'll get it myself.]

819
00:45:50,400 --> 00:45:54,080
[Park Jae Ha: Just use a washed cup.]

820
00:46:18,980 --> 00:46:22,580
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Go over there. You're too close.]

821
00:46:22,580 --> 00:46:25,220
[Park Jae Ha: I'll just sit here.]
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Go over there.]

822
00:46:38,220 --> 00:46:42,740
[Lee Hyeong Jun: I just wondered
what he was going to say again.]

823
00:46:42,740 --> 00:46:46,840
[Park Jae Ha: Are you really not going to
tell me how your date went?]

824
00:46:46,840 --> 00:46:48,940
[Lee Hyeong Jun: It was fun.]

825
00:46:48,940 --> 00:46:50,900
[Park Jae Ha: Yeah?]

826
00:46:50,900 --> 00:46:53,900
[Park Jae Ha: What did you do?]

827
00:46:55,140 --> 00:46:59,860
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Just this and that.]

828
00:46:59,860 --> 00:47:03,780
[Park Jae Ha: Can you give me another chance?]

829
00:47:07,860 --> 00:47:14,300
[Park Jae Ha: I don't know
what you're thinking, and what you'll do,]

830
00:47:14,300 --> 00:47:17,580
[Park Jae Ha: but during this stay here,]

831
00:47:17,600 --> 00:47:24,440
[Park Jae Ha: I really want to
go on at least one date with you.]

832
00:47:33,780 --> 00:47:41,440
[Park Jae Ha: If you don't want to be
miserable, I'll make sure you won't be.]

833
00:47:41,440 --> 00:47:47,720
[Lee Hyeong Jun: I can't answer you right away.]

834
00:47:47,720 --> 00:47:50,800
[Lee Hyeong Jun: I need time.]

835
00:47:53,900 --> 00:47:57,640
[Park Jae Ha: I'm sad seeing you like this.]

836
00:47:59,060 --> 00:48:05,560
[Park Jae Ha: Even though I'm the reason why.
That's how I feel.]

837
00:48:05,560 --> 00:48:10,940
[Park Jae Ha: If you think that
the only way for you to feel better]

838
00:48:10,940 --> 00:48:14,820
[Park Jae Ha: is to completely]

839
00:48:14,820 --> 00:48:17,500
[Park Jae Ha: end things with me,]

840
00:48:17,500 --> 00:48:25,660
[Park Jae Ha: I'll be sad but I'll accept it,
even if we stay here.]

841
00:48:25,660 --> 00:48:30,460
[Park Jae Ha: But I want to be with you.]

842
00:48:34,540 --> 00:48:40,100
[Park Jae Ha: There are
many things I want to do with you.]

843
00:48:40,100 --> 00:48:44,420
[Lee Hyeong Jun: I was curious
what else Jae Ha wanted to say.]

844
00:48:44,420 --> 00:48:47,260
[Lee Hyeong Jun: He asked me
to give him one last chance]

845
00:48:47,260 --> 00:48:51,420
[Lee Hyeong Jun: and if
I could go on a date with him.]

846
00:48:51,820 --> 00:48:56,500
[Lee Hyeong Jun: So I thought
I should go on a date with Jae Ha next time.]

847
00:49:06,940 --> 00:49:11,900
[Can't stop sighing]

848
00:49:17,020 --> 00:49:21,340
[Their hearts are still blazing
in this winter night]

849
00:49:37,660 --> 00:49:40,420
[Cho Yun Jae: Is that coke?]
[Lee Hyun Jun: No, it's coffee.]

850
00:49:40,420 --> 00:49:43,580
[Cho Yun Jae: Coffee? Where did you get it?]
[Lee Hyun Jun: Kanu Coffee.]

851
00:49:43,580 --> 00:49:47,620
[Cho Yun Jae: Oh, really?]
[Lee Hyun Jun: Yes, from Block B.]

852
00:50:02,780 --> 00:50:04,900
[Lee Hyun Jun: Humidifiers.]

853
00:50:04,900 --> 00:50:06,980
[Cho Yun Jae: They arrived?]
[Lee Hyun Jun: Yeah.]

854
00:50:06,980 --> 00:50:08,100
[Cho Yun Jae: Why's it so small?]

855
00:50:08,100 --> 00:50:10,220
[Lee Hyun Jun: Let's leave
one on your side, and one on mine.]

856
00:50:10,220 --> 00:50:12,340
[Cho Yun Jae: Yeah?]

857
00:50:12,340 --> 00:50:15,820
[Cho Yun Jae: Do I have any space for it?]

858
00:50:15,710 --> 00:50:16,730
Thank you.

859
00:50:20,290 --> 00:50:21,190
Thank you.

860
00:50:42,300 --> 00:50:47,580
[Lee Hyun Jun: Is it not working?]
[Cho Yun Jae: It's working. Oh, no, it's not.]

861
00:50:48,500 --> 00:50:51,180
[Cho Yun Jae: Come to think of it,]

862
00:50:51,180 --> 00:50:53,980
[Cho Yun Jae: we don't really talk much,]

863
00:50:53,980 --> 00:50:59,180
[Cho Yun Jae: so why do I like him?
I had some doubts,]

864
00:50:59,180 --> 00:51:03,380
[Cho Yun Jae: but I also wanted to
try to talk with him as much as possible.]

865
00:51:03,820 --> 00:51:06,980
[Cho Yun Jae: Can I ask you something?]
[Lee Hyun Jun: What is it?]

866
00:51:06,980 --> 00:51:12,780
[Cho Yun Jae: Is it OK if I ask you out on a date?]
[Lee Hyun Jun: Yeah!]

867
00:51:12,780 --> 00:51:16,020
[Cho Yun Jae: Really? I heard
we'll get to choose our dates freely,]

868
00:51:13,350 --> 00:51:13,680
Yeah.

869
00:51:16,020 --> 00:51:19,060
[Cho Yun Jae: but we haven't been on a date.]
[(Nods)]

