[Kim Su Min: My worries?]

1515
01:30:16,280 --> 01:30:18,860
[Kim Su Min: My worries...]

1516
01:30:21,040 --> 01:30:24,960
[Unable to say it easily]

1517
01:30:25,960 --> 01:30:32,120
[Kim Su Min: I was just thinking about
what I should say to you.]

1518
01:30:32,880 --> 01:30:35,760
[Kim Su Min: I hope you can
use the gift I gave you here]

1519
01:30:35,760 --> 01:30:40,760
[Kim Su Min: and leave with the memories.]

1520
01:30:40,760 --> 01:30:48,200
[Kim Su Min: Cherish the moments in here
and bring them home with you.]

1521
01:30:48,200 --> 01:30:50,840
[Kim Su Min: That's why I gave it to you.]

1522
01:30:51,400 --> 01:30:55,160
[Kim Su Min: Take great photos with it.]
[Kim Sun Wook: We've to take photos together too.]

1523
01:30:55,160 --> 01:30:59,680
[Kim Su Min: Yeah.
And capture your other moments too.]

1524
01:30:59,680 --> 01:31:02,720
[Kim Su Min:
I hope you keep it and take it with you.]

1525
01:31:02,720 --> 01:31:05,360
[Kim Sun Wook: From tomorrow onwards,
I think I'll bring it everywhere with me.]

1526
01:31:05,360 --> 01:31:09,000
[Kim Su Min: You didn't use it today, right?]
[Kim Sun Wook: Yeah.]

1527
01:31:09,400 --> 01:31:13,120
[Take it out tomorrow.]

1528
01:31:16,120 --> 01:31:18,840
[Su Min only has eyes for Sun Wook]

1529
01:31:18,960 --> 01:31:24,000
[Kim Su Min: What I regretted most
was being passive]

1530
01:31:24,000 --> 01:31:28,480
[Kim Su Min: and not proactively chasing him.]

1531
01:31:29,520 --> 01:31:33,720
[So I mustered up my courage.]

1532
01:31:34,320 --> 01:31:39,080
[Always watching Sun Wook intently
from a distance]

1533
01:31:39,840 --> 01:31:44,960
[Su Min just wants to get closer to him]

1534
01:31:45,560 --> 01:31:51,360
[Despite being slow and clumsy,
they were all moments filled with courage]

1535
01:31:56,840 --> 01:32:01,560
[Will Sun Wook's heart ever align with Su Min's?]

1536
01:32:02,400 --> 01:32:06,420
[Su Min's winter night
filled with courage and wishes]

1537
01:32:06,420 --> 01:32:12,380
[Men's House]

1538
01:32:16,560 --> 01:32:19,960
[Kim Su Min: We're back.]
[Eum Hyeok Jin: You're back.]

1539
01:32:24,750 --> 01:32:26,390
We've got texts.

1540
01:32:33,640 --> 01:32:40,560
[With the Heart Cards numbered 1 to 10,
rank everyone in order of interest
and convey it through the mailbox.
The results will determine who will be eliminated.]

1541
01:32:41,840 --> 01:32:45,120
[The atmosphere becomes heavy]

1542
01:32:48,200 --> 01:32:49,520
[Kim Han Gyeol: I was so shocked.]

1543
01:32:49,520 --> 01:32:52,080
[Kim Han Gyeol: Oh, the producers are great
at manipulating our dopamine levels,]

1544
01:32:52,080 --> 01:32:55,160
[Kim Han Gyeol: catching us off guard
while we were having fun.]

1545
01:32:55,160 --> 01:32:58,920
[Kim Han Gyeol: When we got the text,
it was total silence.]

1546
01:32:58,920 --> 01:33:03,240
[Lee Hyun Jun: Everyone fell silent
and there was a lot of sighing.]

1547
01:33:03,640 --> 01:33:07,720
[Lee Hyun Jun: An elimination this early?]

1548
01:33:08,120 --> 01:33:10,680
[Lee Hyeok Jin: Eliminating someone already?]

1549
01:33:10,680 --> 01:33:13,680
[Lee Hyeok Jin: My first thought was
that I was likely]

1550
01:33:13,680 --> 01:33:16,120
[Lee Hyeok Jin: to be up for elimination.]

1551
01:33:16,840 --> 01:33:19,320
[Oh Min Seong: Is this a survival show?]

1552
01:33:19,320 --> 01:33:21,720
[Oh Min Seong: Why are there eliminations
in "His Man"?]

1553
01:33:21,720 --> 01:33:24,520
[Oh Min Seong: Is it supposed to be so scary?]

1554
01:33:25,000 --> 01:33:29,640
[Lee Hyeong Jun:
No matter who leaves, I'd be sad.]

1555
01:33:30,040 --> 01:33:35,920
[Kim Sun Wook: Oh? So it's not
voting for one person, but ranking everyone.]

1556
01:33:35,920 --> 01:33:38,640
[Kim Sun Wook: So I was at a loss.]

1557
01:33:39,120 --> 01:33:44,280
[Cho Yun Jae: I thought that the ranking itself]

1558
01:33:44,280 --> 01:33:49,320
[Cho Yun Jae: would be so hard to decide.]

1559
01:33:49,690 --> 01:33:55,210
[Kim Su Min: I thought that to some of them,
I might be a potential candidate for elimination.]

1560
01:33:55,810 --> 01:33:58,980
[Park Jae Ha: From the moment I got the text,]

1561
01:33:58,980 --> 01:34:03,450
[Park Jae Ha: I thought
I might really be eliminated.]

1562
01:34:04,320 --> 01:34:08,720
[Taichi: It was so soon.
I think I'm at a disadvantage,]

1563
01:34:08,720 --> 01:34:11,230
[Taichi: so I suddenly got anxious.]

1564
01:34:11,830 --> 01:34:13,300
[Eum Hyeok Jin: It's really here.]

1565
01:34:13,300 --> 01:34:15,300
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I tend to jump to conclusions,]

1566
01:34:15,300 --> 01:34:17,830
[Eum Hyeok Jin: so I thought it might be me,]

1567
01:34:17,830 --> 01:34:20,170
[Eum Hyeok Jin: and I got really anxious.]

1568
01:34:23,570 --> 01:34:26,840
[Their fates will be decided
through the interest rankings]

1569
01:34:28,180 --> 01:34:31,900
[Who will leave Men's House?]
